---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '@/components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Electricity Load Calculator"
  description="Terms and conditions for using the Electricity Load Calculator. Calculations are for informational purposes only — always consult a certified electrician for physical installations."
  keywords="electricity load calculator terms, terms of use, disclaimer"
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Terms & Conditions' }]} />
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-8 md:pt-12 pb-12 md:pb-16 animate-slide-up">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-text-primary">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Terms & Conditions</h1>
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-text-muted">Last updated: June 08, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-base leading-relaxed">
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            By accessing and using the Electricity Load Calculator website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by these terms, please do not use this service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">1. Use of the Calculator</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            The calculations, metrics, and estimates provided by Electricity Load Calculator are intended for informational and preliminary planning purposes only. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            While we strive for accuracy using standard industry averages for appliance wattages, every electrical setup is unique. The tool should be used as a guide, and professional advice from a certified electrician or engineer must be sought for actual electrical planning, sizing of generators/transformers, or major installations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">2. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS. WE EXPRESSLY DISCLAIM ALL WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, WHETHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, THE IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT. WE MAKE NO WARRANTY THAT THE CALCULATIONS WILL BE 100% ACCURATE OR ERROR-FREE.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">3. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            In no event shall Electricity Load Calculator, its developers, or affiliates be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of your access to, use of, or inability to use the site and the calculations provided. This includes, but is not limited to, damages related to electrical failures, equipment damage, or financial losses based on the estimates provided by this tool.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">4. Third-Party Links & Advertising</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            Our website displays advertisements provided by third-party networks, such as Google AdSense. We do not endorse the products or services advertised. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Furthermore, our site may contain links to external websites that are not operated by us. We have no control over the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services and assume no responsibility for them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            The design, layout, look, appearance, and graphics on this website are owned by or licensed to us. Reproduction is prohibited other than in accordance with standard copyright laws. The default appliance database is compiled from publicly available average metrics and is not subject to exclusive copyright, but the presentation and software logic remain our intellectual property.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">6. Modifications to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            We reserve the right to modify these terms from time to time at our sole discretion. Changes will take effect immediately upon posting to the website. Therefore, you should review these pages periodically.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">7. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            If you have any questions regarding these Terms & Conditions, please contact us via our <a href="/contact-us" class="text-text-primary hover:text-accent underline decoration-border underline-offset-4">Contact page</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
